# === Skills scope guard ===
# Only the memory-system core skills ship in this repo. Prevents accidental
# commits of non-core skills dropped into .claude/skills/ during development.
# To add a new core skill, append it here.
.claude/skills/*
!.claude/skills/bridge-promote-insight/
!.claude/skills/contradict-check/
!.claude/skills/crystallize-playbook/
!.claude/skills/knowledge-compile/
!.claude/skills/knowledge-lookup/
!.claude/skills/knowledge-qa-file-back/
!.claude/skills/knowledge-review/
!.claude/skills/session-memory-compile/
!.claude/skills/session-memory-review/

